title: ‘Curb Your Enthusiasm’ Season 11 Premiere
description:
The Ringer’s Bill Simmons is joined by Joe House to discuss the Season 11 premiere of ‘Curb Your Enthusiasm’ (0:30). They choose their favorite scenes (11:25), the funniest bits (17:48), and their cast and non-cast MVPs (23:10).
Hosts: Bill Simmons and Joe House
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
